The '''Alderaanian armed forces''' was the military organization tasked with defending [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]].

==History==
On the day of the end of the [[Alderaan Ascendancy Contention]], fifteen-year old [[Pello Scrambas]] joined the armed forces. Years later, the [[Royal Alderaan Civil Fleet/Legends|Royal Alderaan Civil Fleet]] was formed to protect Alderaan during the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]] and the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It is unclear what relation it had to the rest of Alderaan's military.

